      "content": "A small coastal village where the river meets the sea.\n\nThis tutorial teaches **recipes and crafting** — combining items to create new ones. Find the right ingredients and craft a fishing rod to catch your dinner.\n\nType `inventory` to check what you're carrying."
    },
    {
      "kind": 30078,
      "tags": [
        [
          "d",
