          "item",
          "30078:<PUBKEY>:tides-end-09-recipes:item:hook"
        ]
      ],
      "content": "Coarse sand stretches in a long curve between dark rocks and the restless sea. Kelp and driftwood lie in tangled lines where the last high tide left them. Gulls wheel overhead, their cries thin against the wind.\n\nAn **iron hook** glints among the pebbles, half-buried in the wet sand.\n\nThe dock lies west along a rocky path, and the village is east through the dunes."
    },
    {
      "kind": 30078,
      "tags": [
        [
          "d",
