        ],
        [
          "exit",
          "west"
        ]
      ],
      "content": "A modest square of packed earth ringed by low stone buildings with slate roofs. A dry fountain stands in the centre, its basin cracked and filled with windblown leaves.\n\nThe cobbled road slopes south toward the dock. To the west, a gap between the houses opens onto dunes and the sound of surf."
    },
